<h5>Drop kick</h5>

<p>Drop kicks are used to start or restart the game or when winning a dropout 22. Players may also score a drop goal at almost any point in the match.</p>

<p>From a kick off or dropout you will need to kick the ball high to allow your teammates time to get underneath it to contest for the catch. You may also aim for it to either land in some space or to target a player that is exposed or isn't good at catching.</p>

